<h4>cash application</h4>
<h5>{{appError}}&nbsp;</h5>
{{input type="text" value=subName placeholder="input name for category"}}
<button {{action "addTopCat" subName }}>add category</button>
<hr>
<p>Choose date for your operations</p>
Dates for your new transactions: {{date-picker date=dateStore.nowDate valueFormat='YYYY-MM-DD'}}

<hr>

<ul>
{{#each model as |el|}}
	{{#if el.top}}
		<li>
			<ul>{{recursive-category —ÅategoryId = el.id }}</ul>
		</li>
	{{/if}}
{{/each}}
</ul>

<h4>History of operations</h4>
<p>This is graphic can show for you your history of operations from start date to end date</p>
<p>you can switch this dates</p>
Start date of history of operations: {{date-picker date=dateStore.startDate valueFormat='YYYY-MM-DD'}}
End date of history of operations: {{date-picker date=dateStore.endDate valueFormat='YYYY-MM-DD'}}
<hr>
{{ pie-chart startDate=dateStore.startDate endDate=dateStore.endDate startRender=dateStore.startRender categories=model.length }}

